<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #87CEFA, #00BFFF);
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .sidebar {
            background: #1E90FF;
            color: white;
            width: 50%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            left: -50%;
            animation: slideIn 1s forwards;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            to {
                left: 0;
            }
        }

        .sidebar h3 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .sidebar p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .main-content {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .form-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 90%;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 24px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #00BFFF;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .form-group input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: border 0.3s ease;
        }

        .form-group input:focus {
            border-color: #00BFFF;
            outline: none;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: #00BFFF;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #1E90FF;
        }

        p {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #f7f4f4;
        }
        h4{
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
        }
        a {
            color: #00BFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        a:hover {
            color: #1E90FF;
        }

        .footer {
    background: #f1f1f1;
    color: #555;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.footer h5 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.footer-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 50px; /* Space between the sections */
    flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allows wrapping on smaller screens */
}

.social-links, .contact-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px; /* Space between items within each section */
}

.footer a {
    color: #0970d7;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.footer a:hover {
    color: #0970d7;
}

        h3 {
    font-family: "Lucida Handwriting", "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
        }
        h5{
                color: #000;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h3 style="margin-top: -30px;">Welcome to ArtZone</h3>
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-top: -10px;">
            <img src="img1_dbms.jpg" alt="Art example" style="width: 300px; height: 500px; margin-right: 20px;">
            <p style="margin: 0;">
                Explore, discover, and purchase unique pieces of art from talented artists worldwide. Follow the guidelines to ensure a smooth and enjoyable experience on our platform. <br>If you a new user, please SignUp!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
    
    
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="form-container">
            <h2>Login</h2>
            <form action="/login" method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name:</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="username" placeholder="Enter your name" required autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Login</button>
            </form>
            <h4>Don't have an account? <a href="/signup">Signup</a></h4>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <h5>Designed and developed by:</h5>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="social-links">
                LinkedIn
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pooja-kns-209425244/" target="_blank">Pooja K N S</a> |
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/svishakh/" target="_blank">S Vishakh</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-info">
                Contact: 
                <a href="mailto:poojakns04@gmail.com">poojakns04@gmail.com</a> |
                <a href="mailto:svishakh17@gmail.com">svishakh17@gmail.com</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
</body>
</html>
